{"id":"guide/understanding-communicating-with-http","title":"了解使用 HTTP 与后端服务通信","contents":"<div class=\"content\">\n  <h1 id=\"understanding-communicating-with-backend-services-using-http\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"1z3u8zvhhoar09xqua5gnqgus\">了解使用 HTTP 与后端服务通信<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/understanding-communicating-with-http#understanding-communicating-with-backend-services-using-http\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"cyllngi7g8now7nyzf1erbj5s\">大多数前端应用都要通过 HTTP 协议与服务器通讯，才能下载或上传数据并访问其它后端服务。Angular 给应用提供了一个 HTTP 客户端 API，也就是 <code>@angular/common/<a href=\"api/common/http\" class=\"code-anchor\">http</a></code> 中的 <code><a href=\"api/common/http/HttpClient\" class=\"code-anchor\">HttpClient</a></code> 服务类。</p>\n<h2 id=\"prerequisites\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"e44b21uig1fakj5vcfuvz1bdu\">前提条件<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/understanding-communicating-with-http#prerequisites\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"1mcguuy84a1ltfk4ksodb8v1t\">在使用 <code><a href=\"api/common/http/HttpClientModule\" class=\"code-anchor\">HttpClientModule</a></code> 之前，你应该对下列内容有基本的了解：</p>\n<ul>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"78gqqpxnzs5bqi8d4zmijgaes\">TypeScript 编程</li>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"d61exg56xvc01v8biqt4lzob5\">HTTP 协议的用法</li>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"29peedffjewxu5x1iry7bqfm6\">Angular 的应用设计基础，就像<a href=\"guide/architecture\">Angular 基本概念</a>中描述的那样</li>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"1b72hf0merf2gcrnthuyuzp8v\">Observable 的技术和运算符。请参阅 <a href=\"guide/observables\">Observables 指南</a>。</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"http-client-service-features\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"dubnzi6umb9w8yc39hzpifjgx\">HTTP 客户端服务特性<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/understanding-communicating-with-http#http-client-service-features\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"4qxc6hb42sgwwz0fzeak98140\">HTTP 客户端服务提供了以下主要功能。</p>\n<ul>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"cnhvju4ojbomulycltcr0gjik\">请求<a href=\"guide/http-request-data-from-server\">类型化响应对象</a>的能力</li>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"a9ilig81uj0vndbbk8fk7yztq\">管道式<a href=\"guide/http-handle-request-errors\">错误处理</a></li>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"dzfwr8mgwnbocnhylooqjcqr9\"><a href=\"guide/http-test-requests\">可测试性</a>的特性</li>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"3c6ynycbh1su13xb64z2vgwlf\">对请求和响应的<a href=\"guide/http-intercept-requests-and-responses\">拦截</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"whats-next\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"407r2fj2mi5kvg7imj9zdcpe\">下一步呢？<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/understanding-communicating-with-http#whats-next\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"4x4r50i8eetzljix1n1m0x61d\"><a href=\"guide/http-setup-server-communication\">服务器通信设置</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n  <div class=\"reviewed\">最后复查时间：Wed Aug 16 2023</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/common/http\n - api/common/http/HttpClient\n - guide/architecture-next-steps\n - guide/developer-guide-overview\n - guide/docs-style-guide\n - guide/example-apps-list\n - guide/http-server-communication\n - guide/npm-packages\n - guide/pipes\n - guide/rx-library\n - gu